graph TD
    subgraph "Windows Server (Agent Side)"
        A[storcli64.exe] -->|API/CLI Call| B{UserParameter}
        B -->|raid.pd.discovery| C[LLD: 磁碟自動發現]
        B -->|raid.pd.status| D[PD: 實體碟狀態]
        B -->|raid.vd.status| E[VD: 虛擬碟狀態]
        B -->|raid.roc.temp| F[ROC: 晶片溫度]
    end

    subgraph "Zabbix Server (Processing)"
        C -->|JavaScript| G["解析 JSON 取出 {#SLOT}"]
        G -->|產生| H[Item Prototypes]
        D -->|Regex| I[過濾: Onln/Fail/Rbld]
        E -->|Regex| J[過濾: Optl/Dgrd/Pdgd]
        F -->|數值| K[溫度監測]
    end

    subgraph "Triggers & Actions"
        I -->|Status <> Onln| L[[告警: 磁碟異常]]
        J -->|Status <> Optl| M[[告警: RAID 降級]]
        K -->|> 75°C| N[[告警: 晶片過熱]]
    end

    style L fill:#f96,stroke:#333
    style M fill:#f96,stroke:#333
    style N fill:#f66,stroke:#333
